PRI setPanelColorBitsForRC(pPwmFrame, nPanelRow, nPanelCol, rBit, gBit, bBit) | nBffrR, nBffrC, isRGB2, byteIdx, maskBitsBGR, bitsBGR, currByte, showDebug
